<h2 align="center" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 255);"><big>EJB Component
Model<br>
</big></h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<big><big><big><span style="font-weight: bold;">Important Parts in EJB
Component Model:</span></big></big></big><br>
<ul>
<font color=red>
  <li><big><big><big>Enterprise Beans:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</big></big></big></li>
</font>
  <ul>
    <li><big><big>re-usable
server-side components that clients can remotely access.
      </big> </big></li>
    <li><big><big>Package as ejb-jar file with deployment descriptor file.</big></big></li>
    <li><big><big>Compose and Deploy in EJB container.</big></big></li>
  </ul>
</ul>
<div style="margin-left: 80px;"><big><big>eg., Online Shopping cart,
payment
process.</big></big><br>
</div>
<ul>
<font color=red>
  <li><big><big><big>EJB Container:&nbsp;</big>&nbsp;</big>&nbsp;&nbsp;</big></li>
</font>
  <ul>
    <li><big><big>exist on the
server-side of an enterprise and the "Enterprise Bean" is deployed in
it.</big></big></li>
    <li><big><big>Responsible for all low level functionality.
      </big></big></li>
  </ul>
</ul>
